text: Neuenkirch is a municipality of the district of Sursee in the canton of Lucerne in Switzerland. ==Villages== Sempach Station, Hellbühl, Nellen, Werligen, Klosterhöfli, Klösterli, Lippenrüti, Trutigen, Sellenboden, Neuhus, Weiherhüsli, Rippertschwand, Helfenstegen, Moosschür, Wartensee, Adelwil, Gottsmännigen, Mettenwil and Brämenstall. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Municipalities in Sursee
title: Neuenkirch
